description: You will have a 1:1 one-hour Zoom meeting with me where I review your photos and give you an in-depth portfolio review and mentorship, with demos and tutorials. You can ask me any questions.

My most in-depth program where you will be coached by me for 6-months through weekly group coaching. If you want to transform your photos and achieve your dream in photography, this 6-month coaching program is for you. If you want to learn more about this program, you can check out this one-hour free training.

If you want to learn the most powerful post-processing workflow that transform RAW file into super-sharp noise-less images while being natural and contest-compliant, this Dynamic Tension Stacking program is for you.
